reviewText: Excellent--very well explained, and the videos are very clear. Basic techniques are explained that will help create lei from whatever kinds of flowers--even leaves!--that are available. Great even for those of us on the mainland.
This DVD is filled with a lot of good stuff.  I highly recommend!
Such an amazing DVD worth every penny Mahalo Kuana!
This DVD is amazing! :) Finally a really clear understanding on how to Haku.
Fantastic  video, step by step instructions and creative approach to lei making.
Awesome DVD, great instruction and worth every penny!
